Welcome to Our Restaurant Management System

Explore our seamless online ordering and management system designed to enhance your dining experience.

Core Features

  • Track Orders in Real-Time: See updates as they happen.
  • Integrated Shopping Cart: Manage what you're ordering in a click.
  • Dynamic Order Management: Adjust orders on-the-fly from any device.
  • Menu Customization: Update and customize menu items based on availability.
  • Session Management: Keep your data safe during your ordering process.

Ready to Order?

Browse our Menu Items to start adding to your cart.

Manage your orders and view past transactions on the Orders page.

Track your order in real-time on the Track Order page.

Got questions or need assistance? Visit our Help section.

); } export default Home;
